data.description: Welcome to your new home in the heart of convenience and luxurious living! The perfect starter home or long term investments, this charming 3-level townhome provides the perfect blend of space and comfort for your lifestyle.   Situated in a community with an HOA that caters to your every need, enjoy exclusive access to amenities such as a sparkling swimming pool, scenic nature trail, a dog park for your furry friends, and a clubhouse for social gatherings.  Step inside and be captivated by the custom granite flooring that graces the interior, creating an ambiance of sophistication. The spacious walk-in closet in the Owner Suite offers flexibility for custom closet design, while the garage with a parking pad ensures easy parking solutions.  Relax and entertain on the second-level patio, a private oasis just steps away from your living space. Beyond the comfort of your home, explore the vibrant surroundings minutes away from the Kennesaw Marketplace featuring Whole Foods Market, dining, and an array of amenities. Nearby, discover Towne Center at Cobb, LA Fitness, and a swift 5-minute drive to I-75, providing easy access to the city and beyond.    Nature enthusiasts will appreciate the proximity to Kennesaw Mountain, offering morning hikes and scenic views. With countless shopping and dining experiences along Barrett Pkwy, this townhome is not just a residence; it's a gateway to a vibrant and convenient lifestyle. Don't miss out, schedule a showing today and make this townhome your key to unmatched living.
